  "html_size": 198902,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110162448910\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110162448910\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'7367_9';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<DIV class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">\r\n<DIV class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">\r\n<DIV class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">\r\n<DIV class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">\r\n<DIV class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">\r\n<DIV class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">\r\n<DIV class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">\r\n<DIV class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: #000000\"></SPAN></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: #000000\"></SPAN></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: #000000\">[키가 안크는 이유//키한의원/소아성장]</SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"><STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #e97d81\"></SPAN></STRONG></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"><STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #e97d81\"></SPAN></STRONG></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"><STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #e97d81\">아이들이&nbsp;키가 안크는 이유에는 어떤게 있나요</SPAN></STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #e97d81\">?</SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #e97d81\"></SPAN></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">&nbsp;선천적 요인은 유전요인으로 부모님의 키가 작은 경우입니다. </SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">후천적 요인은 영양, 운동, 수면, 스트레스 및 환경 등 노력하면 개선할 수 있는 요인들이죠. </SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">외국의 연구결과를 보면 성장에 영향을 주는 요인들은 다음과 같습니다. </SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; mso-hansi-font-family: HCI Poppy; mso-ascii-font-family: HCI Poppy\">영양 31%, 환경 26%, 유전 23%, 운동 20%</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">따라서 아이가 키가 작고 성장이 느리다면 영양, 운동, 환경(수면, 스트레스)을 개선해 주어야 합니다. </SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">&nbsp; </SPAN><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp; <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130310_205/isuhani_136291895469431omu_PNG/%BC%BA%C0%E5%C2%F7%C6%AE1.PNG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"519\" height=\"357\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 519px; rheight: 357px\" id=\"20130310_205/isuhani_136291895469431omu_PNG/%BC%BA%C0%E5%C2%F7%C6%AE1.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A631920E')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130310_205/isuhani_136291895469431omu_PNG/%BC%BA%C0%E5%C2%F7%C6%AE1.PNG?type=w3\"></P><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 바탕\"></SPAN>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 바탕\"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">&nbsp;</P><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) -->\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"><STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #e97d81\">어떤 경우에 성장 치료가 필요한가요?</SPAN></STRONG></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">평균신장보다 10cm 이상 키가 작은 아이</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕\">1년에 4cm 미만의 속도로 자라는 아이</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">또래보다 키가 많이 작으면서 소화기 질환(식욕부진, 소화불량, 복통, 설사, 변비 등), </SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">잦은 호흡기 질환(감기, 천식, 비염 등) 등이 있는 아이</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">또래보다 키가 작으면서 소아비만인 아이</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">&nbsp; </SPAN><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">&nbsp; </SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130310_240/isuhani_13629100930660S1Or_PNG/%BC%D2%BE%C6%BC%BA%C0%E52.PNG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"352\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 620px; rheight: 397px\" id=\"20130310_240/isuhani_13629100930660S1Or_PNG/%BC%D2%BE%C6%BC%BA%C0%E52.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A631920E')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130310_240/isuhani_13629100930660S1Or_PNG/%BC%D2%BE%C6%BC%BA%C0%E52.PNG?type=w3\"></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"><STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #e97d81\">소아성장 치료는 어느 시기에 하는게 좋나요?</SPAN></STRONG>&nbsp;</SPAN></P><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 바탕\">\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><BR style=\"CLEAR: both\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">남자는 14세 이전, 여자는 12세 이전에 하는게 좋습니다. </SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">사춘기(2차성징)이 끝나는 남 16세, 여 14세가 넘어가면 성장판이 거의 닫히기 때문에 성장치료의 효과를 기대하기 어렵습니다.</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">&nbsp;남자는 음모가 자라고 변성기가 오기 전에, 여자는 초경을 시작하기 전에 해야 합니다. 연령에 따라 성장치료의 방법도 달라집니다. </SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"></SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<DIV class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center></DIV></SPAN>&nbsp; </DIV>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130310_194/isuhani_1362919015194444eA_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2_%BC%BA%C0%E5%C5%AC%B8%AE%B4%D0%C7%A511111%BC%D2%BE%C6%BC%BA%C0%E5%B5%BF%B1%D7%B6%F3%B9%CC%C7%A5111.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"367\" height=\"359\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 367px; rheight: 359px\" id=\"20130310_194/isuhani_1362919015194444eA_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2_%BC%BA%C0%E5%C5%AC%B8%AE%B4%D0%C7%A511111%BC%D2%BE%C6%BC%BA%C0%E5%B5%BF%B1%D7%B6%F3%B9%CC%C7%A5111.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A631920E')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130310_194/isuhani_1362919015194444eA_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2_%BC%BA%C0%E5%C5%AC%B8%AE%B4%D0%C7%A511111%BC%D2%BE%C6%BC%BA%C0%E5%B5%BF%B1%D7%B6%F3%B9%CC%C7%A5111.jpg?type=w3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) -->\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"><STRONG><U><SPAN style=\"COLOR: #3a32c3\"><U>한의학적 성장치료는 성장호르몬의 분비를 촉진시켜 성장에 도움을 주는 한약을 기본으로 합니다. </U></SPAN></U></STRONG></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"><STRONG><U><SPAN style=\"COLOR: #3a32c3\"><U>그러나 한약을 통한 성장치료의 진정한 장점은 성장방해요인들까지 해결해준다는데 있습니다. </U></SPAN></U></STRONG></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; mso-hansi-font-family: HCI Poppy; mso-ascii-font-family: HCI Poppy\">예컨데 소화기가 약해서 잘 안먹으려 들고 자주 체하고 </SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; mso-hansi-font-family: HCI Poppy; mso-ascii-font-family: HCI Poppy\">설사나 변비가 있는 타입은 소화기를 튼튼히 하는 약재를 써서 소화기까지 치료하는 것입니다. </SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; mso-hansi-font-family: HCI Poppy; mso-ascii-font-family: HCI Poppy\">신경이 예민해서 밤에 잠을 깊이 못 자고 스트레스를 잘 받는 아이는 신경을 튼튼하게 해 주는 방법을 써야 하지요.</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; mso-hansi-font-family: HCI Poppy; mso-ascii-font-family: HCI Poppy\">호흡기가 약해서 감기에 잘 걸리고, 비염이 있는 아이라면 호흡기를 튼튼하게 해야 하죠.</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">&nbsp; </SPAN><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 휴먼명조; mso-hansi-font-family: HCI Poppy; mso-ascii-font-family: HCI Poppy\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"><U>한의학은 키&nbsp;크게하는 무슨 약, 감기에 무슨 약 하는 식으로 일률적으로 정해진 처방을 쓰는 것이 아닙니다. </U></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=바탕글 style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 휴먼명조; mso-hansi-font-family: HCI Poppy; mso-ascii-font-family: HCI Poppy\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"><U>환자의 체질과 증상에 따라 가장 알맞은 방법을 찾는 것을 변증논치라고 하는데 이것이 한의학의 기본 정신입니다. </U></SPAN>\r\n<DIV class=autosourcing-stub-saved style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"></DIV>\r\n<DIV class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\"></DIV></SPAN>&nbsp; \r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P></DIV>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130310_63/isuhani_1362919045599zJyLG_PNG/%BC%D2%BE%C6%BC%BA%C0%E5.PNG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"309\" height=\"424\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 309px; rheight: 424px\" id=\"20130310_63/isuhani_1362919045599zJyLG_PNG/%BC%D2%BE%C6%BC%BA%C0%E5.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A631920E')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130310_63/isuhani_1362919045599zJyLG_PNG/%BC%D2%BE%C6%BC%BA%C0%E5.PNG?type=w3\"></P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #ff0000; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff\"></SPAN></STRONG>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #ff0000; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff\">[키에 대한 잘못된 상식]</SPAN></STRONG></P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><U><SPAN style=\"COLOR: #ff0000\"><U><SPAN style=\"COLOR: #e573ae\"><U><SPAN style=\"COLOR: #cfcca2\"><U><SPAN style=\"COLOR: #acacac\"><U><SPAN style=\"COLOR: #7d7d7d\"><U>살이 키로 간다?</U></SPAN></U></SPAN></U></SPAN></U></SPAN></U></SPAN></U></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><U><SPAN style=\"COLOR: #ff0000\"><U><SPAN style=\"COLOR: #e573ae\"><U><SPAN style=\"COLOR: #cfcca2\"><U><SPAN style=\"COLOR: #acacac\"><U><SPAN style=\"COLOR: #7d7d7d\">&#65279;<U>&#65279;</U></SPAN></U></SPAN></U></SPAN></U></SPAN></U></SPAN></U></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>비만 즉 과도한 지방축적은 키가 크는데 오히려 방해가 된다.</P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>살이 키로 간다는 말은 사춘기에 이르러 급성장을 보이기 직전에 체중의 증가를 보이기 때문에 나온 말 일것이다.</P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>부족한 영양도 지나친 영양도 키 크는 데에는 좋지 못한 영향을 준다</P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>이수한의원에서 성장클리닉은 체형교정으로 바른자세를 유지할수 있도록 도와줌으로써</P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>키크기에 한층 더 효과를 높여줄 수 있습니다</P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><STRONG><SPAN style=\"COLOR: #3a32c3\">성장체형교정/성장한약/성장침</SPAN></STRONG></P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><pzp-pc-layout class=\"_naverVideo _vnl\" vid=\"D674E3B2CBC703766408841250A5D3CD5526\" key=\"V127156eb980e609ebac356e9be4b1ee33e3d39ebd99e3fff7bba2fa04e7186edb9c856e9be4b1ee33e3d\" outKeyMode=\"false\" hasLink=\"true\